title: Stray Review Round Up - Kinda Funny Games Daily 07.18.22
description:
Janet and Tim round up the rounds ups! We talk Stray reviews, As Dusk Falls Reviews, and get into God of War Ragnarok's story. 

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:04:30 - Housekeeping

The Gamescast is a double dose of reviews this morning! We’ve got Stray and As Dusk Falls thoughts from Greg, Bless, Andy, and SnowBikeMike!

After this episode of KFGD, we’re doing a PuzzleQuest 3 Sponsored stream before some KFW shenanigans. Come join the kingdom and win some codes! Live on Twitch, later on youtube.com/kidnafunnyplays


Thank you to our Patreon Producers: FargoBrady, Gordon McGuire, & Al Tribesman

The Roper Report  -
00:06:50 - Stray Review Round-Up: Metacritic 84
00:18:50 - As Dusk Falls Review Round-Up: Metacritic 76 on Xbox Series X
00:27:39 - Coming to Game Pass
00:35:20 - Ad
00:38:35 - God Of War Ragnarok Website Updated With New Story Details - George Foster @ The Gamer
00:44:56 - Soulframe looks like Warframe crossed with Princess Mononoke
00:56:00 - Out today
00:56:20 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Greg and Gary
